payload.message:
Use an accessible selector, not the dynamic `id`.

Best options in Playwright:

```ts
// Most stable: linked label text
const addressInput = page.getByLabel(/address/i);

// If it's the only autocomplete/combobox in that area
const addressInput = page.getByRole("combobox", { name: /address/i });
```

Then interact:

```ts
await addressInput.fill("1600 Pennsylvania");
await page.getByRole("option", { name: /1600 pennsylvania ave/i }).click();
```

If there are multiple “Address” fields, scope to a container first:

```ts
const section = page.getByTestId("shipping-address");
await section.getByLabel(/address/i).fill("...");
```

